reviews.content:
This show is a strange one. Each season is diferent, so i have to rate them diferently.Season 1 gets 10 stars;
Season 2 gets 3 stars;
Season 3 gets 9 stars;
Season 4 gets 6 stars.Explanation for season 1 rating:
Amazing. The acting, the mystery, unpredictability, the plot... Simply amazing. And it's also quite funny.Explanation for season 2 rating:
Boring and uninteresting. I stopped watching after a few episodes and thought it will be the last season of this show. Nothing "FARGO" about it.Explanation for season 3 rating:
Almost as good as season 1. Great acting, yet not as great plot. Also has a little of that anti-russian propaganda sprinkled on top.Explanation for season 4 rating:
It's okay. Just okay. The underlying plot was interesting, but it was executed poorly. But there is nothing "FARGO" about it.
